  ],
  "remarks": "East Oil & Gas Production Company (EOGPC) is a subsidiary of the Iranian Central Oil Fields Company (ICOFC) which in turn is a subsidiary of the National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC). The National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC) is a State-owned and operated entity providing substantial financial resources and support to the Government of Iran. Therefore, EOGPC is owned or controlled by an entity providing support to the Government of Iran.",
